      <title>波兰股市领跌，反映俄罗斯风险不断升级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/polish-stocks-lead-selloff-as-proxy-for-escalating-russian-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于俄罗斯扩大使用核武器的范围，投资者将这个东欧国家的资产作为该地区风险升级的代表，导致波兰股票和兹罗提下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/polish-stocks-lead-selloff-as-proxy-for-escalating-russian-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 11:58:49 GMT</pubDate>
